Page_0: "Blane,
   When you get back from Shalebridge tonight, grab a few guys and clean out the barge. The last time I was in the dock area the stench of the rigor mortis was enough to gag a burrick tamer. I know the slave trade has picked up quite a bit, but Truart isn’t going to continue paying top dollar for vagrants who smell like they're already dead. Throw the bodies into the cove and collect any personal effects that may have been left behind by the others. I won’t have our vessels littered with corpses and such. See to it.

-N"